  "text": "Tangential sections of the medial entorhinal cortex and parasubiculum were obtained as previously described [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] by separating the entorhinal cortex from the remaining hemisphere by a cut parallel to the face of the medial entorhinal cortex and sectioning with the surface of the entorhinal cortex attached to the block face of the microtome.",
